snippet.title: Animal Raceway
snippet.description: Animal Raceway Choose your animal and train it to let it compete in sports. When you win, you can leave the island.

snippet.title: Animal Hunter
snippet.description: Animal Hunter Shoot the wildlife in the forest before the time runs out.

snippet.title: Blob Farm
snippet.description: Blob Farm Drag and drop the blobs away from the green slime, bowling balls, rockets, and other dangers.

snippet.title: Kilroy: Chernobyl Farms
snippet.description: Kilroy: Chernobyl Farms 3D first person shooter with excellent graphics. Kill all the murderous mutants.

snippet.title: The Farmer
snippet.description: The Farmer Manage your own farm. Grow and harvest crops, sell chicken eggs and earn big money!

snippet.title: Youda Farmer
snippet.description: Youda Farmer Run your own farm. Grow crops, keep chickens, etc. and provide the shops the supplies they need.

snippet.title: Goodgame Farmer
snippet.description: Goodgame Farmer Farm simulation game. Care for ani- mals, grow crops and earn achievements and upgrades.

snippet.title: Uphill Farmer
snippet.description: Uphill Farmer Ride your motorbike through the country side avoiding sheep. Perform stunts and set the highscore.

snippet.title: Rescue on Cocoa Farm
snippet.description: Rescue on Cocoa Farm Physics puzzle game. Try to get all the chocolate animals back into the barn.

snippet.title: Youda Farmer 2
snippet.description: Youda Farmer 2 Stop the real estate tycoon to save your farm and the village by buying and selling products.
